version_description: More accurate transcription from the live performance including tablature of commonly used walk. Lyrics adjusted from the original version of the song to Moore's slightly different lyrics, including unique spoken intro and outro.

Taken from live performance on the late late show in 2016 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=efibHMLQcos. Had tried following the existing tabs, but thought the timing was always a small bit off so tried following the live performance and think I got close. Christy has a capo in the performance but playing without a capo in standard tuning still fits with the performance.
Based on alvaro-guitar's version. Just includes all the verses.
Change the key to C or use a CAPO on fret 5 to emulate the recording on 'The Has Come Album'.
This exercise has a more accurate and more complete representation to the original song.
